<body>
<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1078764" n="1r"/>
<opener><salute>Viro Eximio at<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> Doctissimo
             <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-102552517" type="person">Petro Antonio Michelotti</rs>
<lb/><abbr>S. P. D.</abbr>
<lb/>Joh. <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Bernoull<choice><orig><g ref="#j">j</g></orig><reg>i</reg></choice></rs>.</salute></opener>
<p>Firmissime constitueram, nisi ad <rs key="B_991170515018905501" type="letter">novissimas meas</rs> ad
             <lb/>Te datas responsionem daturus esses favorabilem et con<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ditionibus a me propositis ex omni parte satisfacien<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tem, me poste<choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> nullis omnin<choice><orig><g ref="#ograv">ò</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice> propositionibus auscultatu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rum sed potius omnia rejecturum, si vel maxim<choice><orig><g ref="#eacut">é</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> tot<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice>
             <lb/>summam 1500 imperialium <hi rend="u">uncialium</hi> promitteretis imo
             <lb/>si eam in duplum etiam augeretis: Interim quia <rs key="B_991170515018905501" type="letter">lit<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>teris illis meis postremis</rs> jam dimissis intellexi dem<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>
             <lb/><choice><abbr>Cl.</abbr><expan>Clarissimo</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-120379260" type="person">Scheuchzero</rs> Viro sane docto et meritissimo spem sub<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>natam esse succedendi <choice><abbr>Cl.</abbr><expan>Clarissimo</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-104265264" type="person">Morgagno</rs> in <rs type="organisation">Cathedram Theo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>retico-Medicam</rs> et quia hunc Virum mihi amicissi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>mum pro Collega habere res mihi foret optatissi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ma, patiar adhuc semel, non obstante Tua responsione
             <lb/>nondum satisfaciente, ut tentes num ad mentem
             <lb/>meam negotium hoc dirigere possis prout inter
             <lb/>nos jam dudum convenit; nam frustra quereris
           <pb facs="1078765" n="1v"/>
<lb/>de ambiguitate thalerorum, cum non tantum per
             <lb/>eos totidem argenti uncias intellexerim, sed etiam di<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>sert<choice><orig><g ref="#eacut">é</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> dixerim (quod Tu Vir <choice><abbr>Cl.</abbr><expan>Clarissime</expan></choice> poste<choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> repetiisti at<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice>
             <lb/>ideo sine ambiguitate percepisti) nimirum sesquimille
             <lb/>Thaleros unciales <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quivalere quadringentis Ludovicis
             <lb/>aureis Gallicis. De c<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>tero me refero ad <rs key="B_991170515018905501" type="letter">pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>cedentes
                <lb/>meas Litteras</rs>, quas si ita lubuerit communicare po<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>teris cum Amplissimo <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089924410" type="person">Ruzzino</rs>, cujus nutui ut et
             <lb/>Tuo desiderio libentissime in omnibus obtemperabo
             <lb/>possibilibus, sed ad hanc rem quod attinet, dispensa<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>bitis ut spero ubi noveritis res meas domesticas non
             <lb/>permittere ut lares mutem alio quam inter nos sti<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>pulato modo, pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>terquam quod de honore meo agi<del>t</del>
<lb/>putem, ne vel terruncio<note type="editorial">Ne teruncius quidem bedeutet soviel wie "nicht ein Heller".</note> <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> promissa salarii quantita<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>te recedam. Quare rogo etiam at<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> etiam ut tandem
             <lb/>abrumpas filum t<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>diosi adeo et diuturni moliminis, si<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>quidem nihil obtinere possis, quod rebus meis sit
             <lb/>conveniens. Jam satis est quod tanto tempore
             <lb/>fuerimus Fortun<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> ludibrium; prim<choice><orig><g ref="#ograv">ò</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Agnatus</rs>
<pb facs="1078766" n="2r"/>
<lb/>meus per aliquot annos ut pila fuit jactatus et
             <lb/>postquam aliquoties spe van<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> lactatus esset, su<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>bito fuit explosus. Nunc ego sat diu in scena ves<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tra <choice><sic>campareo</sic><corr>compareo</corr></choice> protractus ut nostis pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>ter volun<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tatem meam. Date ergo disparendi tandem ve<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>niam: amo tranquillitatem et otium studiis
             <lb/>meis incumbendi: nondum eo adactus sum neces<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>sitatis, ut extra Patriam panem meum er<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rabundus qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>ram hac pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sertim qua sum <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>tate
             <lb/>et valetudine cert<choice><orig><g ref="#eacut">é</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> non nimis firm<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice>.
             <lb/>Vobis non vitio verto quod Parsimoni<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> studeatis
             <lb/>velim igitur vicissim ut meo me genio indulge<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>re sinatis et ne <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>gr<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> feratis quando vide<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tis me constanter repudiantem oblatam quam<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>vis conditionem qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> promissum non ex<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quat.
             <lb/>Melius ita<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> operam Tuam Vir <choice><abbr>Cl.</abbr><expan>Clarissime</expan></choice> collocabis in com<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>mendato <choice><abbr>Celeb.</abbr><expan>Celeberrimo</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-120379260" type="person">Scheuchzero</rs>, qui sine dubio
             <lb/>minori pretio obtineri poterit, nec tamen mino<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ris erit ornamenti et utilitatis in <rs type="organisation">Archilyceo</rs>
<pb facs="1078767" n="2v"/>
<lb/><rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Patavino</rs>, quam vel ego vel quisquam alius.</p>
<p>Ecce <rs key="B_991170515093405501" type="letter">Litteras meas ad ipsum</rs>, quas, quia facultatem
         <lb/>eas legendi Tibi concessit, apertas mitto; sed ro<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>go ut lectas et poste<choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> tuo sigillo signatas ei
         <lb/>quantocyus transmittas quocun<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> in loco jam degat.
         <lb/>Ecce <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Agnati</rs> mei (qui Tibi salutem dicit plurim<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice>)
         <lb/>Responsionem ad Comitis <rs key="pers_DE-588-119543885" type="person">Riccati</rs> <rs key="biblio_QETMIRCN" type="biblio">schediasma</rs> in
         <lb/>Diario Veneto publicatum. Rogamus ut sine mo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>r<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> (nam operam Tuam promisisti) in italicam
         <lb/>Linguam vertas ac versionem in eodem Diario
         <lb/>edi cures; vide autem ut accurat<choice><orig><g ref="#eacut">é</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> prodeat et
         <lb/>pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sertim ut vitia typographica in analyticis
         <lb/>expressionibus pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>caveantur: Ex hoc speci<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>mine videbunt Vestrates, quo jure qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice>ve in<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>juri<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>judicatam habeant opinionem contr<choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice>
         <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Agnatum</rs> meum; sed fort<choice><orig><g ref="#eacut">é</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> tempus aliquando veniet,
         <lb/>quo eo potiundi facultas non amplius dabitur.</p>
<lb/><closer><salute>Vale<supplied>.</supplied></salute> <dateline>Dabam <rs key="place_GEO-2661604" type="place">Basile<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> <choice><abbr>a. d.</abbr><expan>ante diem</expan></choice> <date when="1715-03-27">VI. Kalend. April. 1715.</date></dateline></closer>
